Class Skills

Namespace
CampaignKit.Compendium.DungeonsAndDragons.TomeOfBeasts3
Assembly
CampaignKit.Compendium.DungeonsAndDragons.dll

Represents the skillset of a creature in the Tome of Beasts 3. Each property represents a different skill and its proficiency level.
